    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Service</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">UserService</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@Autowired</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">UserDao</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">userDao</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 容器运行时注入</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>IoC容器的核心职责</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>职责</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>对应接口</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>实例化Bean</td>
          <td>根据配置创建对象</td>
          <td>BeanFactory</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>依赖注入</td>
          <td>装配Bean之间的依赖关系</td>
          <td>AutowireCapableBeanFactory</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>生命周期管理</td>
          <td>初始化和销毁回调</td>
          <td>InitializingBean / DisposableBean</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>作用域控制</td>
          <td>Singleton / Prototype / Request / Session</td>
          <td>Scope</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
