    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">BeanFactory层级：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">BeanFactory（根接口）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
