<h3 id="bean生命周期从定义到销毁的完整过程">Bean生命周期：从定义到销毁的完整过程</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 实例化（Instantiation）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ 反射或CGLIB创建对象
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 属性赋值（Population）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ @Autowired、@Value注入
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 初始化（Initialization）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ BeanNameAware.setBeanName()
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ BeanFactoryAware.setBeanFactory()
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ ApplicationContextAware.setApplicationContext()
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ @PostConstruct方法
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ InitializingBean.afterPropertiesSet()
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ 自定义init-method
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 使用（In Use）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">5. 销毁（Destruction）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ @PreDestroy方法
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ DisposableBean.destroy()
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓ 自定义destroy-method</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Component</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">MyBean</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">implements</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">InitializingBean</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">DisposableBean</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> 
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">ApplicationContextAware</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">BeanNameAware</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@PostConstruct</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">postConstruct</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">System</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;1. @PostConstruct&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@Override</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">afterPropertiesSet</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">System</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;2. InitializingBean.afterPropertiesSet()&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">initMethod</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">System</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;3. 自定义init-method&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@PreDestroy</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">preDestroy</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">System</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;1. @PreDestroy&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@Override</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">destroy</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">System</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;2. DisposableBean.destroy()&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
